cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as aspect term extraction. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves designing a new word embedding method. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as aspect term extraction is a sub-task of information retrieval. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for learning word embeddings.
